  1616 				; ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  1617 				;  LFO (vibrato): a triangle that ramps a signed pitch offset between
  1618 				;  -lfo_max and +lfo_max; rate sets step interval, depth sets amplitude.
  1619 				;  No multiply: lfo_level_u counts 0..2*max, offset = level - max.
